v8:item.v8:content: The user who added the file version.
The universal date when the file version was modified.
Local date and time when the file version was modified.
The date when the file version was added.
The index of the file version icon. An internal field.
The path to the file version in the volume. An internal field.
The file version size in bytes.
The parent version (hierarchical versions structure is possible).
Status of the text extraction. An internal field.
Text extracted from the file. An internal field.
Where the file version is stored: in a volume or in the infobase.
Temporary storage of the file version. An internal field.
Date when a user added the digital signature.
Name of the signature file. An internal field.
Certificate owner details: full name, job title, etc.
The certificate's thumbprint. An internal field.
Signature binary data. An internal field.
Certificate binary data. An internal field.
Date when the signature was last verified.
Flag that indicates whether the signature has passed the validation.
